":"2020-11-25T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"1888debf3ae276f2f6b52da44fdcb53acc14e8ad","tid":2299022,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"是但鳩噏啲藉口無咁搶口"},{"pid":"1cdf6c9fd9b382bab1a569561df05d300fc20759","tid":2299022,"uid":28152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"474e73ac37b3a41d3d8982ce7d542ab9277c4ccb","tid":2299022,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"大家同時喺同一個地點出現<br />\n唔代表大家有過近距離接觸，然後好大機會喺感染者感染到病毒<br />\n<br />\n最多咪事後俾啲科學家用來連下線<br />\n病人A可能係由病人B感染，因為佢哋同時喺某地點出現"}]}